  "texts": [
    "This model utilizes an improved Transformer encoder to effectively capture both character-level and word-level features.",
    "As depicted in the last column of Table I, the existing information extraction techniques for NER are not suitable for financial concept extraction in fund prospectuses.",
    "The first reason is that all these methods are designed to extract short phrases from sentences, such as person names, URLs, times, and places.",
    "For example, a commonly used dataset for training and testing these methods is a dataset such as the CoNLL2003 dataset for NER tasks.",
    "CoNLL2003 covers English and German, including around 14,000 documents for English and 12,000 for German, with an average of 12 to 18 sentences per document."
